1
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:33,330
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:36,250
[Episode 14 Hearts Laid Bare]

3
00:00:39,150 --> 00:00:39,960
Fufeng.

4
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:43,280
Every time we meet,

5
00:00:44,030 --> 00:00:45,490
we always end up in a fight—

6
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,470
you never even give us a moment

7
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:49,710
to catch up.

8
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,030
This time,

9
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:53,930
let's have a proper talk.

10
00:00:56,670 --> 00:00:59,840
I have nothing to say to you.

11
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:36,280
What, can't bear to deal with him?

12
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,200
That really doesn't sound like you.

13
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,200
Do you really have feelings for him?

14
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:46,840
This face of his—
I gave it to him.

15
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:49,380
His heart is yours,

16
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,950
and only that pitiful will of his

17
00:01:54,130 --> 00:01:55,490
is his own.

18
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,610
But unfortunately,

19
00:01:57,789 --> 00:01:59,920
even that is already under my control.

20
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,520
Fufeng.

21
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,079
According to ancient records,

22
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,520
what surges up from the depths
of Yin-Yang Crossing

23
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,590
is not merely corruption,

24
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,190
but pure primordial power.

25
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,970
Why must we keep acting like mere fixers,

26
00:02:30,970 --> 00:02:32,500
endlessly patching it up?

27
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:35,360
Sealing it and guarding Yin-Yang Crossing

28
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,560
is our duty.

29
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,150
Duty?

30
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:38,550
That's just shackles.

31
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,390
If we can control this power,

32
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:42,200
it would go far beyond Yin-Yang Crossing.

33
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,930
We could rebuild order itself—

34
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,750
cleanse this filthy world

35
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:48,070
and bring about a total upheaval.

36
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:52,760
You wouldn't have to be trapped
in this tiny Yin-Yang Crossing.

37
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,920
Fufeng, come with me.

38
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:02,680
Do you understand what it means

39
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,120
to take that step forward?

40
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,800
It means...

41
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,030
I will no longer stay here with you,

42
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,690
guarding Yin-Yang Crossing.

43
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,710
I will prove

44
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:13,550
that my path is the right one.

45
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:23,680
Liu Fufeng,

46
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:26,710
you're nothing more than that after all.

47
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:27,770
Do you really think

48
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,750
escaping Yin-Yang Crossing

49
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,650
means you'll be free as the sky and sea?

50
00:03:34,329 --> 00:03:36,260
The moment I lent you half my heart,

51
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:38,120
I cast the Treebound Curse.

52
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,120
If you dare betray me—

53
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,470
betray Yin-Yang Crossing—

54
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,590
your body

55
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,960
will turn into deadwood.

56
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:52,480
So you were scheming against me
from the very beginning?

57
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,280
I kept a backup plan.

58
00:03:58,710 --> 00:03:59,680
I didn't expect

59
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,400
it would actually come in handy.

60
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,560
Fine.

61
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:07,770
Now that you've lost half your heart,

62
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,860
let's see how long you can hold on.

63
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,430
I'd like to see

64
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:14,190
which of us will have the last laugh.

65
00:04:39,810 --> 00:04:41,810
The Treebound Curse is taking hold!

66
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:43,430
I must replenish my strength

67
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,840
and find a new vessel.

68
00:04:57,820 --> 00:05:00,620
Corrupting power—
this is a gift from the heavens.

69
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,960
With this corrupting power,

70
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,160
I can sustain myself here

71
00:05:05,370 --> 00:05:06,630
until I find a new body.

72
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,000
Bai Han,

73
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,520
you've finally come.

74
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:20,370
Do you see it?

75
00:06:21,210 --> 00:06:22,870
All those countless failures

76
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,380
were just for this moment.

77
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,320
You are not Bai Shanjun—

78
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,310
that was only a name you used briefly

79
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:31,120
when you lost yourself.

80
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,340
Back then, my spirit left my body.

81
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:35,000
I let you take our heart

82
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,430
and leave,

83
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,870
while I stayed behind

84
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,770
to deal with this damned curse.

85
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,780
What you're seeing
isn't someone else's story—

86
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:46,440
these are our memories.

87
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,510
Come back.

88
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,650
Don't resist this natural fusion.

89
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:59,200
No... That's not right.

90
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:12,430
I just want to do my job properly.

91
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,760
Forget it.

92
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:16,800
The three-day deadline has arrived,

93
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,970
and the case remains unsolved.

94
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,230
I will keep my promise—

95
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,990
whether I live or die is up to you.

96
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:21,460
My Lady,

97
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:24,790
what's wrong?
Do you need spiritual power?

98
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:30,070
Nothing will go wrong.

99
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,870
You'll definitely be all right.

100
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:35,120
Don't carry everything alone.

101
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,510
I place my full trust

102
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,159
in you.

103
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:44,800
My Lady,
I hope I can be of use to you.

104
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,830
Bai Shanjun, don't believe him.

105
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:54,010
Look at me. Look at Yin-Yang Crossing.

106
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,270
Your persistence, your sense of justice,

107
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:59,000
everything you've done
to uncover the truth—

108
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:01,990
none of it is anything
like that faithless coward.

109
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,580
I am not you.

110
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,190
I would never harm innocent lives,

111
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:10,190
and I would never betray Lady Fufeng.

112
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:15,480
You've simply forgotten
the most crucial memory.

113
00:08:16,180 --> 00:08:17,560
You've been misled
by her narrow-minded fixation

114
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,850
on staying in one corner of the world.

115
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,570
That's all very normal.

116
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,430
But once you and I merge,

117
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,330
you'll understand everything I've done.

118
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,190
You are me—Bai Han.

119
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:34,380
We have always been one.

120
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,200
Bai Shanjun,

121
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,850
hold on to yourself.
Don't be deceived by him.

122
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,230
No...

123
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:44,710
I am not you.

124
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:56,270
I am not you.

125
00:08:57,630 --> 00:09:00,030
M-My Lady. My Lady.

126
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:01,240
My Lady—

127
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:03,850
strike now! My Lady.

128
00:09:06,070 --> 00:09:07,160
My Lady!

129
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:09,300
Do it!

130
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:22,230
You would rather die
than break a promise,

131
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:24,190
rather shatter than bow.

132
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,640
I must admit, I'm growing

133
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,060
a little more impressed with you.

134
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:34,440
A life-saving grace—so you intend
to repay it with yourself?

135
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:39,030
My Lady, why are you suddenly
so concerned about me?

136
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,910
Because I want you to stay

137
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:43,600
and become mine.

138
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:47,210
Do what you believe in
and what you're best at—

139
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:50,320
uphold justice with clarity,
judge cases with insight,

140
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,870
and protect the peace

141
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:53,680
of those within your reach.

142
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:30,320
As long as corruption does not perish,
neither will I.

143
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,000
Liu Fufeng,

144
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,390
we have a long way to go.

145
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,270
Fengling,

146
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:21,470
how has My Lady
been recovering lately?

147
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:25,560
My master briefly awakened today,

148
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,870
but her spiritual energy is still weak.

149
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:30,330
She is currently resting
in the spirit pool.

150
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,690
Then I'll go in and take a look.

151
00:11:45,730 --> 00:11:46,330
My Lady.

152
00:11:47,630 --> 00:11:48,390
You're here.

153
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:52,670
How is Yin-Yang Crossing now?

154
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,840
The restriction has been lifted.

155
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,700
The people are living in peace—
everything is well.

156
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:03,790
Your heart

157
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,890
has not yet been recovered,

158
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:07,910
but don't worry, My Lady.

159
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,270
I will help you.

160
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:15,320
You are already helping me.

161
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,440
Not enough.

162
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:22,280
It's enough as long as
it's within your power.

163
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,240
My Lady,

164
00:12:23,780 --> 00:12:25,490
you expect too little of me—

165
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:29,780
or rather, you simply don't
trust me enough yet.

166
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,520
Humans and demons are of different paths;

167
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:35,780
everyone has things beyond their reach.

168
00:12:40,750 --> 00:12:44,080
People always say humans and demons
are of different paths,

169
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,170
but what I see in Yin-Yang Crossing

170
00:12:49,110 --> 00:12:52,480
is humans and demons living together
in peace and prosperity.

171
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,680
How can there be any "different paths"?

172
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,150
Perhaps so.

173
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:01,810
Humans and demons may not
be on different paths.

174
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,320
But with different ambitions

175
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,550
and desires,

176
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:10,280
it truly becomes impossible
to walk the same path.

177
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,120
My Lady,

178
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,850
when you once asked me in return

179
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
what it means to be truly willing...

180
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,870
I used to think

181
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:25,880
you meant for me
to willingly stay in Yin-Yang Crossing.

182
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:31,850
But now it seems
I was wrong, wasn't I?

183
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:51,870
Can you guess it now?

184
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,810
When Bai Han possessed me,

185
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,870
I glimpsed his memories—

186
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,360
or more precisely,

187
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:21,040
the memories of this heart.

188
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:28,990
What did you see?

189
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:33,120
I saw him, in order to keep
his spiritual power from dissipating,

190
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,520
plunge into corruption,

191
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:37,880
taking one vessel after another

192
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,300
until he finally found me.

193
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,630
When we first met,

194
00:14:44,230 --> 00:14:45,490
your hatred toward me—

195
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:48,100
was it not only because of this face,

196
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:50,730
but because of this heart as well?

197
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,360
Yes.

198
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:06,200
I wanted to reclaim my heart,

199
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,200
but I couldn't.

200
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,810
Perhaps it had been away
from me for too long

201
00:15:11,810 --> 00:15:14,080
and no longer
recognized its original owner.

202
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:16,210
I was afraid that if you knew the truth,

203
00:15:16,590 --> 00:15:18,850
you would resist and refuse to return it.

204
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,960
So I led you closer to me,

205
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,860
made you accept me,

206
00:15:25,970 --> 00:15:27,090
made you rely on me—

207
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,870
waiting for you

208
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,650
to come to me willingly.

209
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,080
If, when we first met,

210
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:37,150
you had told me the truth,

211
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:40,010
I would never
have tried to possess and cling

212
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,080
to what was never mine to begin with.

213
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:54,750
Bai Shanjun...

214
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:56,280
back then,

215
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:59,150
I didn't understand you.

216
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,440
My Lady.

217
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:04,210
You don't need to give me

218
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,440
such insincere answers now.

219
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:08,370
This isn't you—

220
00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:11,470
and I don't want you to be like this.

221
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:15,710
I say all this today

222
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:17,800
only to tell you:

223
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:20,680
I willingly

224
00:16:22,740 --> 00:16:24,380
return this heart.

225
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:30,550
It's not something you deceived me
into giving up.

226
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:33,720
No matter how you see me—

227
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:36,510
as human, as vessel,

228
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,770
as real or illusion—

229
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,030
I exist because of you,

230
00:16:40,910 --> 00:16:42,000
and I came for you.

231
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:48,750
Fufeng...

232
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:52,870
I am fond of you.

